name: MRJK- 003
description:
taken from the ancient Javanese secret spell book
The ancient Javanese secret spell book raises the phenomenon of spells that are part of the culture and customs of Central Java, Indonesia.
Secret spells are spells that are passed down in secret and from generation to generation to the descendants of the King. ancient Javanese secret spells are closely related to Dabdo Palon, Syekh Subakir, and Syekh Siti Jenar.
